title: RINOS in MAGA Hats
itunes:title: RINOS in MAGA Hats
description:
There are only 15 days left until the most historic and important midterm election of Charlie’s lifetime, and he is calling all conservatives to plan out their voting strategy to avoid any of the Left’s potholes, pitfalls, and shenanigans on November 8th. Charlie warns Republicans about a RINO in sheeps’ clothing, and he also covers Biden’s recent bizarre interview with a "trans activists" TikTok influencer in attempts to help his plummeting approval rating.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
